---
// About Section Component
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">CHI SONO</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image-wrapper">
        <div class="image-frame">
          <img src="/profilo.jpeg" alt="Gerardo Romani" class="profile-image" />
          <div class="image-glow"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-content">
        <h3 class="name-title">Gerardo Romani</h3>
        <div class="name-underline"></div>
        <p class="bio-text">
          Sono un creatore di contenuti appassionato di storytelling visivo. Attraverso i miei video racconto storie che emozionano e ispirano, combinando creativit√† e tecnica per creare esperienze uniche.
        </p>
        
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">50K+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Views</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--darker-bg) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-frame {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
    box-shadow: 
      0 0 20px var(--primary-blue),
      0 0 40px rgba(199, 91, 57, 0.5),
      inset 0 0 20px rgba(199, 91, 57, 0.2);
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .image-frame:hover .profile-image {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(44, 95, 158, 0.3), transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .image-frame:hover .image-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .name-title {
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-blue), var(--primary-blue));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .name-underline {
    width: 120px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-blue), transparent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-gray);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.5);
    border-radius: 15px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(44, 95, 158, 0.3);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .stat-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--primary-blue);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(44, 95, 158, 0.3);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-blue), var(--primary-blue));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .name-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .bio-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
